<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/spotlights/9-18-95/dupont.html 204.71.237.74 19970109113536 text/html 5621
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 11:35:54 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:46 GMT
