<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/spotlights/8-21-95/sp-clc.html 204.71.237.74 19970122013021 text/html 13767
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 01:30:42 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:33 GMT
Content-length: 13580
