<h2>


June 25, 1996


</h2>
<P>
<img src="/townhall/infotain/humor/ccc/962403.gif"><br>
[ <a href="/townhall/infotain/humor/ccc/i-date.html">Index by Date</a> | <a href="/townhall/infotain/humor/ccc/i-sub.html">Index by Subject</a> | <a href="/townhall/infotain/humor/ccc/agree.html">Membership Agreement</a>  ]
