<DOCNO>WT19-B30-77</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA055-000920-B015-419</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/spotlights/9-5-95/houseru.html 204.71.237.74 19970109113844 text/html 14930
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 11:39:00 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:39 GMT
