http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/hall_of_fame/kirk/kirkmem.html 204.71.237.74 19970109115959 text/html 36933
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 12:00:07 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 09-Apr-96 19:06:03 GMT
