<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/spotlights/9-5-95/tyingit.html 204.71.237.74 19970109113813 text/html 12368
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 11:38:31 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:39 GMT
