http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/spotlights/9-18-95/frc-tra.html 204.71.237.74 19970109113456 text/html 4714
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 11:35:17 GMT
