http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/spotlights/8-7-95/army0712.html 204.71.237.74 19970121230730 text/html 19663
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 23:07:53 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:34 GMT
Content-length: 19478
