http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/columnists/howley/howl092695.html 204.71.237.74 19970109151221 text/html 5084
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 15:12:34 GMT
