http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/columnists/dupont/dupo081095.html 204.71.237.74 19970109135802 text/html 5838
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 13:58:19 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 22-May-96 15:28:11 GMT
