http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/columnists/fumento/fume112095.html 204.71.237.74 19970109150804 text/html 6346
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 15:08:13 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 22-May-96 15:48:25 GMT
Content-length: 6158
